@startuml
[*] --> InsertedCard

state InsertedCard
InsertedCard : entry / card inserted
InsertedCard : do / prompt for PIN
InsertedCard : exit / PIN requested

InsertedCard --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

state WaitingForPIN
WaitingForPIN : entry / nil
WaitingForPIN : do / wait for PIN entry
WaitingForPIN : exit / PIN entered

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN

state ValidatingPIN
ValidatingPIN : entry / nil
ValidatingPIN : do / verify PIN
ValidatingPIN : exit / PIN verified or not

ValidatingPIN --> Verified : [PIN verified]
ValidatingPIN --> NotVerified : [PIN not verified]

state Verified
Verified : entry / PIN verified
Verified : do / provide transaction options
Verified : exit / user selects option

Verified --> ProcessingWithdrawal : withdrawal selected
ProcessingWithdrawal : entry / nil
ProcessingWithdrawal : do / process withdrawal request
ProcessingWithdrawal : exit / cash dispensed

ProcessingWithdrawal --> DispensingCash : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash

state DispensingCash
DispensingCash : entry / withdrawal request processed
DispensingCash : do / dispense cash
DispensingCash : exit / cash dispensed

DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt

state PrintingReceipt
PrintingReceipt : entry / cash dispensed
PrintingReceipt : do / print receipt
PrintingReceipt : exit / receipt printed

PrintingReceipt --> ReturningCard : Receipt Printed / Return Card

state ReturningCard
ReturningCard : entry / nil
ReturningCard : do / return card
ReturningCard : exit / transaction completed

ReturningCard --> Resetting : [Transaction Completed]

state Resetting
Resetting : entry / nil
Resetting : do / reset system
Resetting : exit / system ready for next user

Resetting --> [*] : After (Elapsed Time) / Ready for Next User

state NotVerified
NotVerified : entry / PIN not verified
NotVerified : do / prompt user to re-enter PIN
NotVerified : exit / PIN re-entered

NotVerified --> ValidatingPIN : [PIN re-entered]

@enduml
